# encrypy

To encrypt a file:

```bash
encrypy encrypt secrets.txt -o secrets.enc
```

To decrypt the file:

```bash
encrypy decrypt secrets.enc -o secrets.txt
```

If the encrypted file was a Python script, you can also run it encrypted:

```bash
encrypy run myscript.enc
```

